Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.45,0:01:33.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.71,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aku menemukanmu, Yuri! Shiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.50,0:01:49.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata begitu, Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.59,0:01:53.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar wanita jalang pengkhianat!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.90,0:01:57.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, karena aku tidak bisa menemanimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.02,0:02:00.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti berat, ya. Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.30,0:02:04.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, mereka anak kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.70,0:02:06.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.05,0:02:09.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,sudah menjadi ayah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gumpalan daging macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.32,0:02:22.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu akan menjadi makananku?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.16,0:02:28.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya menginginkanmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.27,0:02:32.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiro! Cepat serahkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.43,0:02:39.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serahkan tubuhmu padaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.74,0:02:47.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuhmu berbeda dari yang lain.\NMereka tidak tahan lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.47,0:02:50.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku jadi teringat masa lalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.63,0:02:58.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu itu aku belum mengerti,\Ntapi sekarang sudah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.21,0:03:03.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku selalu ingin menjadi manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.29,0:03:10.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bilang, ini Rinka yang Yuri katakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.34,0:03:14.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau terus begini, Yuri dalam bahaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.71,0:03:19.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan sekadar Rinka.\NApi ini sudah membuatnya terpesona.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.21,0:03:23.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat lakukan, Okumura!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, gagal.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepalaku dipenggal si kakek,\Nrasanya benar-benar gila.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sampai tidak ingat apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.82,0:03:56.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Si kakek tua bangka dan nenek itu menghalangiku,\Njadi butuh waktu sampai kekuatanku kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.87,0:04:01.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, percobaan pertama biasanya\Nmemang tidak berjalan lancar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Niko.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.27,0:04:08.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Obaba.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.59,0:04:11.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.24,0:04:17.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dipikir-pikir,\Nitu memang kegagalan yang diperlukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.83,0:04:21.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya demi mengarahkan pada dirimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin menjadi dirimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.70,0:04:27.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dirimu yang dicintai Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.39,0:04:30.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku iri padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.67,0:04:31.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.42,0:04:38.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cemburu dan frustrasi...\NKarena kamu merebutnya dariku!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.43,0:04:39.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru kamu yang merebutnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu juga sama, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita itu sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akuilah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita itu
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bikin kesal saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya aku sudah merasukimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa juga...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.42,0:05:27.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.65,0:05:33.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang mau disamakan denganmu, keparat!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.95,0:05:43.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia malah bunuh diri!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.17,0:06:00.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak! Shiro! Tidak!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.37,0:06:09.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.89,0:06:20.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,menjadi pria yang kamu cintai.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana? Kamu senang, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.79,0:06:32.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini demi dirimu yang kucintai!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu adalah dirimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.42,0:06:47.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tahu rasanya sakit,\Ntakut akan kematian,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.69,0:06:51.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan kesepian, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.95,0:06:55.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal tahu rasanya semua itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,kenapa malah menyakiti orang lain?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.41,0:07:06.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebaiknya jangan memaksakan diri.\NKamu bisa mati karena pendarahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.71,0:07:10.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kembalikan...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus bicara dengannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kembali...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kembalikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.18,0:07:24.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.97,0:07:27.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mencintaimu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satan, hentikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.06,0:07:34.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu tidak mencintaiku?\NKembalikan cintaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perasaanmu itu
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,bukan cinta!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.87,0:08:02.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri... tidak akan kubiarkan mati!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu itu cuma tahu merebut sesuatu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah batasmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.92,0:08:17.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enyahlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.15,0:08:33.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kondisimu lebih mengkhawatirkan darinya.\NAku akan mempercepat masa nifasmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tahanlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar bodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa juga yang rela mati demi monster itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.59,0:08:51.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku itu mantan subjek eksperimen Elixir.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pemulihanku lebih cepat dari orang biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.75,0:08:58.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa menyatukan\Nkulit bekas tebasan dalam satu jam.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.46,0:09:01.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi itu berisiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.61,0:09:05.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya dia belum lenyap\Nkalau caranya seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.49,0:09:08.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia akan kembali cepat atau lambat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, ada Shemihaza rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Apa? Jadi dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu lumayan beruntung, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.54,0:09:23.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Energi Shemihaza\Nbisa mempercepat kinerja sel.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lukanya sudah tertutup!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.57,0:09:30.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malam ini, selain aku,\Nsemua anggota Grigori terluka parah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.49,0:09:33.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paladin, Arc Knight,\Nserta banyak pendeta dan Eksorsis
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.95,0:09:37.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,telah dilahap api biru dan tewas.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.81,0:09:45.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri Egin, semua ini terjadi karena Satan\Nmenginginkanmu dan terus mencari tubuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.74,0:09:51.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengingat besarnya kehancuran ini,\Nsebagai Eksorsis,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.96,0:09:55.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku ingin kamu mengorbankan diri\Ndemi memutus obsesi Satan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak-anakku...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.99,0:10:06.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keberadaan yang bisa memicu obsesi Satan\Nsebaiknya dibunuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.78,0:10:09.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, sampai kita memahami\Ncara mengeksorsisnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak ada pilihan selain merawatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bawa dia dengan hati-hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.39,0:10:15.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.54,0:10:16.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu berniat menghalangi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak bersalah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.56,0:10:26.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan soal siapa yang salah.\NKenyataannya memang begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu ada di hadapan Grigori!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minggir!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.58,0:10:32.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.58,0:10:35.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak akan kubiarkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beraninya menodongkan pistol pada Grigori!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kamu paham konsekuensinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa berdiri?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan membiarkanmu mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bergerak!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.80,0:10:55.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perbuatanmu ini sudah termasuk pengkhianatan!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Buka pintunya dengan kunci ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.36,0:11:11.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, bukannya kamu ingin\Nmenyaksikan semuanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mohon maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cukup.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu yakin?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.65,0:11:27.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masih ada hal lain yang harus kulakukan.\NSeharusnya kamu juga sudah paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,mungkin saja perempuan itu sudah...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terlalu dekat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.55,0:11:49.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini di mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.31,0:11:53.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kantor cabang kesatria\Nyang ditutup sejak lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.07,0:11:59.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di dekatnya ada menara pengawas Yeti,\Nsekarang jadi tempat persembunyian.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita pindah begitu badai salju mereda.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini tempat rahasia,\Njadi bisa dipakai untuk sementara.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu memang suka tempat persembunyian, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.51,0:12:13.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Be-Berisik! Biarkan saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.87,0:12:15.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.79,0:12:19.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.93,0:12:24.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, mereka menangis bareng!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.63,0:12:29.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Si kembar memang suka ada ikatan batin.\NMungkin mereka kedinginan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.02,0:12:33.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau mencari pakaian dulu.\NUsahakan apinya tetap nyala.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.58,0:12:42.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah, sudah.\NAku harus kasih kalian nama dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.75,0:12:43.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.04,0:12:44.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.35,0:12:49.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menemukan camilan!\NMeski bajunya lusuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu sedang apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyusui.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Susu...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.62,0:12:59.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka sedang menyusu di dalam baju.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serius? Berarti kamu harus makan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.77,0:13:07.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah memikirkan nama mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.21,0:13:10.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak yang berapi-api ini seperti Rinka.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti Rin.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asal-asalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asal-asalan banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.47,0:13:19.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, yang kecil ini seperti Yukiotoko,\Nberarti Yukio.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.90,0:13:23.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.07,0:13:28.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nama Rin masih masuk akal,\Ntapi Yukio dari mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.78,0:13:32.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, kamu bercanda, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.59,0:13:37.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bercanda!\NYukiotoko itu berarti hangat dan kuat!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.92,0:13:41.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daripada itu, kenapa tidak dimakan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku sudah berbaik hati padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga, padahal biasanya kamu jahat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, sekarang kamu berutang budi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuh, kan, jahat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.99,0:14:00.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Badai saljunya sudah mereda.\NMenara pengawasnya jadi kelihatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempat persembunyianku\Nada listrik, air, dan makanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebaiknya kita pergi sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.96,0:14:06.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.10,0:14:13.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku sedikit pusing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo berangkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya tidak usah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah mendingan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.47,0:14:26.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.78,0:14:30.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Be-Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu fokus berjalan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.97,0:14:34.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.25,0:14:43.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial! Biasanya lima belas menit juga sampai\Nkalau tidak ada salju.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukannya ada Yeti di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.49,0:14:49.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya mereka sudah musnah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.29,0:14:52.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kantor cabang\Ndan menara pengawasnya kosong.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah sampai persembunyian,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.06,0:15:04.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bersembunyi dulu dan mengawasi keadaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.11,0:15:08.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sambil mencari\Ntempat persembunyian selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.23,0:15:11.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.49,0:15:15.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu malah jadi buronan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru aku merasa lega.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.53,0:15:22.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena selama ini aku ingin bebas.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya aku begini dari awal.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kali ini, kita akan tinggal bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang menjadi ayah,\Nkamu jadi ibunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.51,0:15:40.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyenangkan, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.03,0:15:54.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.54,0:15:56.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan indah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.14,0:16:03.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.11,0:16:14.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenagaku hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.25,0:16:23.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiro, gendong aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar kamu ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin mengajak Shura juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan banyak minta!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.57,0:16:37.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, dia menganggapku tunangannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.05,0:16:44.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, aku yang menjadi ayah pun\Nsudah tidak masuk akal.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya bingung harus bagaimana.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.03,0:16:55.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti kita main lempar kacang saat musim semi,\Nkamu yang jadi roh jahatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.51,0:16:56.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.02,0:17:02.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin melihat sakura yang mekar.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pergi ke pantai saat musim panas,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.81,0:17:11.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan makan semangka\Nsambil melihat kembang api.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.73,0:17:18.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita akan makan makanan lezat\Nyang banyak saat musim gugur,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.45,0:17:23.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan tidur di kasur yang hangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.22,0:17:31.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu merayakan ulang tahun\Nsaat musim dingin,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan kamu
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadilah ayah
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang sesuai kamu inginkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemudian
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.85,0:17:45.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,suatu saat
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.63,0:17:48.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,kamu akan menjadi
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,ayah yang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.13,0:18:00.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, asalkan ada kamu, pasti...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.06,0:18:04.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.93,0:18:06.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.97,0:18:08.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu baik-baik saja?\NTinggal sedikit lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.86,0:18:10.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertahanlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rin.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yukio.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai saudara,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalian harus akur, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.57,0:18:50.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei! Tunggu dulu! Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang benar saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masih hangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumohon! Aku mohon!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.95,0:19:08.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga mencintaimu\Nsejak pertama kali kita bertemu!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.71,0:19:22.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,kamu mendengarku?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.88,0:19:30.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak rela.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.91,0:19:35.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sudah tidak mendengar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal barusan kamu masih tertawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.43,0:19:45.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sudah pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.69,0:19:58.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa...?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa...?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.78,0:20:05.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak lebih...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Andai aku...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya salahku!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata masih ada yang hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudahlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.63,0:21:27.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mati seperti ini saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.67,0:21:34.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku bisa bersikap lebih baik
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan bisa melindunginya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.91,0:21:41.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku membiarkannya\Nmenderita dan mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.18,0:21:45.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Monster pun kalah berengsek
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.37,0:21:49.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,dari bajingan sepertiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.42,0:21:55.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,sudah
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak punya apa-apa lagi.
